Program: Discovery
Title: Predicting Behaviour
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrypk
Last Broadcast Date: 11 May 2004
Investigation into the ability of predicting human behaviour and the 'theory of mind'. We do it unconsciously, that is attempt to make sense of what others are doing and also predict what they are about to do. The programme looks at new insights into what it means to be a fully-functioning social being. Show less